When an issue contains an error message (such as a dependency violation), bringing up a modal (such as the "Review and Commit Changes" modal) causes the error message to be displayed on top of the modal - making it appear as if the error message is part of the modal and the lightbox.

The error message should appear beneath the modal.

Browser: Chrome 53, Chrome 56. JIRA version is 7.3.1.

