As Portfolio user I want that epics which are currently in progress (yellow JIRA category) would be scheduled before open epics (blue category), so that when presenting the roadmap I show most accurate plan for all the epics in the scope and how ongoing epics impact retst of the plan.

In order for Portfolio to calculate schedule closer to the reality it should consider status when calculating timeline and resource allocation for epics. In multi-project portfolio with multiple Kanban teams, open epic might get scheduled before the epic currently in progress.

