Hi, 

I really think that the start date in Portfolio for JIRA needs to be configurable by the user.  It just doesn't make sense that the start date of my epics automatically updates to the date of the current day calculation!  It causes our entire organization to lose the historical view or all our projects.  I understand that Portfolio is supposed to help estimate and plan for projects going forward, but I find that when the start date of my epics in Portfolio keep adjusting to the current day, it doesn't actually reflect reality.  It looks like all the company projects just started today, and then the progress bar makes it seem we are performing well.  

Is this something that can be fixed please. I've read many forums that have asked for this as well.

